      "id": "meal-prep-sunday",
      "title": "My Simple Sunday Meal Prep Routine",
      "excerpt": "Spend 2 hours on Sunday to make your weeknights so much easier. Here's exactly what I do.",
      "content": "Sunday meal prep doesn't have to be complicated. Here's my simple routine:\n\n## 1. Plan the Week (15 minutes)\nWrite down 5 dinner ideas. That's it. Not 7 - just 5. The other nights are for leftovers or simple scrambles.\n\n## 2. Grocery Shop (45 minutes)\nOrder online or hit the store with your list. Stick to the perimeter - produce, meat, dairy.\n\n## 3. Prep Basics (1 hour)\n- Wash and chop vegetables\n- Cook a batch of rice or quinoa\n- Bake a tray of chicken\n- Hard boil eggs\n\nThat's it! You're set for the week.",
